<dl id="n06055i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06055i">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06055i"> 55(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Trist has a black mask</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Un masque aussi avait &eacute;t&eacute; plac&eacute; parmi les feuilles lustr&eacute;es et les baies rouges du houx. &ldquo;Quand donc me regarda-t-il pour la premi&egrave;re fois, <mark>ce masque terrible</mark> &hellip; <font color="green">[A mask had also been placed among the lustrous leaves and red berries of the holly. When was he looking at me for the first time, this terrible mask ...]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 150</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c01126e" href="c01all.htm#c01126e">VI.C.01:126(e)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
